The paper deals with reinforcement learning, inverse reinforcement learning, and transfer learning, which are all subfields of machine learning. The use of generative adversarial networks (GANs) and the options framework also suggest a focus on deep learning and robotics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
